{"title":"长城二题","authors":["叶延滨"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":11,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城二题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶延滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山丹·祁连山马场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这才是龙的故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祁连雪闪着神话的银光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原夏怒放七色的野花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙者，神马也"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山丹马天下美名扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马啊，华夏民族的图腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮过五千年战争史文明史 　（连《西游记》也让马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮西天取经的行囊）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马后有青铜的战车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马前有五色的旌旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听长箫与鼓角中的画卷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读夜光杯和琵琶声中的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当长城在一万次黑云中苍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马儿却永远咴咴嘶鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬生命之鬃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋青春之蹄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山丹马是雪山之魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山丹马是草原精血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看万马奔腾时你才真正懂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那只马踏飞鸟的青铜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是文物，是华夏梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题金昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座有色金属的新城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城的邻居，金昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是地图上长城凸凹线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗结实的铆钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盘火红的熔炉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熔岁月锈铁之箭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后羿射日之箭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熔历史折断之戟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉唐边塞之戟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铸我们新的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铸国歌铿锵音符"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的长城是你是我更是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的血肉我们的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的计算机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的装配线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——啊，长城已成为背"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说岁月漫长说历史悠久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说明天的地平线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于新的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新长城有着血色的朝霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有着金属的光泽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时，且莫忘了金昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个光荣的铆钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一枚骄傲的城徽"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}